name: collections::vec_deque::VecDeque::<T, A>::push_front_mut

collections::vec_deque::VecDeque::<T, A>.doc: Returns `true` if the buffer is at full capacity.

Returns the index in the underlying buffer for a given logical element
 index - subtrahend.

Writes an element into the buffer, moving it and returning a pointer to it.
 # Safety
